Package: mare
Title: Microbiota Analysis in R Easily
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-04-13
Author: Katri Korpela
Maintainer: Katri Korpela <katri.korpela@helsinki.fi>
Description: This package processes 16S amplicon reads produced by Illumina MiSeq or HiSeq and visualises and analyses the resulting data. The package utilises the USEARCH software to process the reads.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.1)
LazyData: true
Imports:
	R2admb,
	devtools,
	R2admb,
	vegan,
	sp,
	gstat,
	Hmisc,
	beanplot,
	stringr,
	MASS,
	seqinr,
	ggplot2,
	reshape2,
	fgui,
	Biostrings,
	ShortRead,
	BiocGenerics,
	glmmADMB,
	gplot,
	qgraph
